## WHAT EACH ENGINE FILE DOES (quick reference)

| File | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| `scanner.py` | Clone repo, run Semgrep, normalize output |
| `classifier.py` | Map Semgrep rule IDs → bug type keys |
| `probability_model.py` | P(exploit) from bug type + exposure |
| `impact_model.py` | 5-component financial impact calculation |
| `expected_loss.py` | EL = P × Impact, Priority = EL / hours |
| `ranker.py` | Sort results by priority score |
| `explainer.py` | Generate management-readable explanation |

