## KNOWN LIMITATIONS (be honest in demos)

- Probability values are calibrated estimates, not live threat intel
- Impact assumes 20% record exposure (configurable)
- Semgrep misses some logic bugs by design (it's static analysis)
- All numbers should be treated as order-of-magnitude, not actuals

